If you have any questions or comments, PLEASE leave them, because this is my first 
tab and it's likely I made mistakes. Also, if you're here, it's probably because you 
also fell in love with this song, and we should all try to collectively tab it to perfection
to do it justice! I hope this tab is helpful~! ^^=